column5: Got out on the bud and marys party boat caught tons of fish.  Lots of bait.....blue runners  the missus caught a huge mutton snapper.....  and heres the haul for the day  awesome time in two days we've both caught seven different species of fish.  On sunday we've got a back country charter booked report to follow.....
Did ya feed the tarpon while you were there?
awesome...nice haul.  i went on one of those in Ft laud
